science fiction conventions.

00:00:38.350 --> 00:00:41.910
But it's definitely
exploded since the internet,

00:00:41.910 --> 00:00:46.340
The internet is like the primary
social forum for furries.

00:00:46.340 --> 00:00:50.570
The textbook definition
is "an animal

00:00:50.570 --> 00:00:52.150
with human characteristics".

00:00:52.150 --> 00:00:54.763
