to think of it as more

00:00:54.763 --> 00:00:57.080
just a bunch of monster people.

00:00:57.080 --> 00:00:58.980
It's really hard to
pin down one thing,

00:00:58.980 --> 00:01:01.090
because there's so many
different types of people.

00:01:01.090 --> 00:01:03.630
